data.description: Huge price reduction!!! The motivated seller also is willing to pay $3,000 toward the buyer's closing costs, prepaid or rate buy down with a full price offer. This beautiful renovated home with so much character has a lot to offer. Gorgeous tiles just was laid down in living room, kitchen, dining room, utility room, entrance and bedrooms hallway. Granite counter tops in the kitchen and secondary bath room. Gourmet chef kitchen has double oven, cook top and lots of cabinets. Large size bedrooms. The secondary bedrooms are sharing a Jack n Jill bathroom. The specious living room features an exquisite bar, gas burning fire place, and built in cabinets. Decently sized back patio with fully covered pergola is a perfect place to relax and enjoy the professionally landscaped yard. Minutes away from Lake Hefner biking & walking trails, Nature parks, Kilpatrick turnpike , shopping and restaurants. Home is nested on about quarter of an acre lot and is great for entertaining. Hot tub in the back patio is being sold "as is".
